            <sentence id="1.2">In Bamboo, we are not able to build with mvn due to encoding problems, e.g.:</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="3">
            <sentence id="3.1">A bit of research shows this is not uncommon, and that the mvn-compiler-plugin configuration needs to be updated to include an *encoding* reference, e.g.,</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="5">
            <sentence id="5.1">Source: http://stackoverflow.com/questions/1562843/howto-use-maven-in-a-heterogenous-environment-with-different-encodings</sentence>
